== Welcome to Foodogle

Foodogle is a website dedicated to food lovers. This website allows the user to:

1. Search for Recipes by Name
2. Search for Recipes by Ingredients
3. Add new Recipes with images
4. Add new Cuisines
5. List Recipes based on Cuisines
6. List all Recipes
7. List all Cuisines
8. Share recipes on various social networks
9. Recommend recipes on Google


Data Model:

Each Cuisine has multiple Recipes. Every Recipe can have multiple ingredients.

Installation Instructions:

https://info.sv.cmu.edu/do/view/CurriculumLogistics/RubyOnRailsInstallation#Install_GIT_client_source_control
